snippet.title: Super Mega Baseball 4 (PC) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of 2023's Super Mega Baseball 4, PC version (on Medium quality basically, high was just a little choppy for me). I chose two of the "Legends League" teams that include real (retired) players like David Ortiz and Bartolo Colon, a first for the Super Mega Baseball series.
